      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable work horse or a budget-friendly commuter. While the engine and transmission are functional, the engine shows signs of minor oil seepage and the suspension feels somewhat loose over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, and the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done but will eventually require some maintenance attention to keep it in peak form.",
