      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and sophistication. It maintains a commanding presence, characterized by a well-preserved exterior and a meticulously kept cabin. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical integrity, this model offers a seamless synthesis of performance and long-term value. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that has been maintained to an exacting standard.",
