      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed thanks to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential and comprehensive subframe reinforcement. Recent mechanical stewardship includes a VANOS overhaul and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within factory tolerances. This example offers a tactile analog experience with the mechanical integrity demanding enthusiasts expect.",
