    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new adventure! It\u2019s been a super reliable car for me, perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in great shape and has been really well-loved, so you can expect a smooth drive and a clean interior. There\u2019s plenty of life left in this beauty\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
