      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically robust, showcasing linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional torque vectoring and tactile feedback. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced to improve torsional rigidity, and a comprehensive Vanos refresh was recently completed to ensure precise camshaft timing. Additionally, rod bearings were replaced as a proactive measure. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering the quintessential balance of lateral grip and chassis composure. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the mechanical vitals are optimized for spirited driving.",
